# moleculer-{{ project_name }}
This is a [Moleculer](https://moleculer.services/)-based microservice.

## NPM scripts

- `npm run dev`: Start development mode (with hot-reload & REPL, port 3000)
- `PORT=3001 npm run dev`: Same as above but using port 3001
- `npm run start`: Start production mode, defaults to port 3000
- `npm run build:docker`: Build Docker image

